Detailed Description

The TSeparatorKit class provides a set of others TSeparatorKit and TShapeKit nodes with a transform and a tracker.

The TSeparatorKit structure: 

  CLASS TSeparatorKitt
  -->"this"
        "callbackList"
  -->   "topSeparator"
  -->      "pickStyle"
  -->      "appearance"
  -->      "units"
  -->      "transform"
  -->      "texture2Transform"
  -->      "childList"
  -->"tracker"
